                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-319-victim2628 t18320906-319-viclabel1806"></join>, <placeName id="t18320906-319-crimeloc1807">Judd-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320906-319-crimeloc1807" type="placeName" value="Judd-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320906-319-crimeloc1807" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-319-off1804 t18320906-319-crimeloc1807"></join>. I saw the prisoner in our shop with a female, and while she was looking at some ribbon, I saw him take a roll of ribbon from the drawer, and put it down, in the act, as I supposed, of giving it to the female who stood by him; I immediately caught hold of his arm, asked what he was going to do with it, and said, "We must keep a sharp eye on him;" he made no answer - he left the shop very shortly after; the female bought nothing - I told Mr. Green what I had seen; he followed, and took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-319-person2630">
                  THOMAS 
                  WINSTEAD GREEN
               <interp inst="t18320906-319-person2630" type="surname" value="WINSTEAD GREEN"></interp>
